CHANGES
=======

v1.1.5
------

* version: Bump version to v1.1.5
* antibot: Add some new ETH/investment scam keywords
* config: Add a unified config upgrading path
* config: Move v3 data migration helpers into main v3 migrate function
* antibot: Remove redundant handling code for InputUser resolve failures
* bot: Allow customizing message response mode
* system: Use common command result path for restart status message
* bot\_setup: Fix timeout/exception handling and use tuple for fututes

v1.1.4
------

* version: Bump version to v1.1.4
* antibot: Blacklist "talk with you in private"
* snippet: Bump snippet replacement delay to 1 second

v1.1.3
------

* version: Bump version to v1.1.3
* antibot: Add more suspicious keywords
